Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.97,0:01:39.94,logo2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}SGS曙光社\Nhttp://bbs.sgsub.com/
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.87,0:01:37.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且也许还能弄清
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.37,0:01:39.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们遇到的青年的身份呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.23,0:01:44.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呀 基尔巴特
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.06,0:01:58.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,金色的头发 翠绿的眼瞳
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.26,0:02:00.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奥兹?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.59,0:02:01.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.98,0:02:06.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的名字是 杰克
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.10,0:02:08.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杰克·贝萨流士
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.51,0:02:16.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\3c&H666666&\b0\pos(319,372)\blur7}赤色独眼的恶魔
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.31,0:02:44.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那孩子总是孤单一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.62,0:02:48.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明我和人偶们都陪在她身边
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.30,0:02:51.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她却一直看起来很寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.03,0:03:04.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,疼…疼…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.47,0:03:06.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,直到那一天
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.24,0:03:09.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙到来之时…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.25,0:03:17.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,疼…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.52,0:03:23.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的像只猫一样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.77,0:03:26.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就是一只猫
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.29,0:03:27.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一贯如此
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.89,0:03:29.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唉 这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.66,0:03:32.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么我就该向你的饲主提意见了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.61,0:03:34.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你居然把未来的公爵大人的脸
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.89,0:03:37.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弄成这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.00,0:03:42.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是没教养
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.09,0:03:45.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,磨爪子应该在合适的地方呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.60,0:03:51.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真是个怪人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.42,0:03:53.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伤成这样还能笑得出来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.07,0:03:57.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明是自己的事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.78,0:03:59.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,却似乎漠不关心
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.33,0:04:02.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你明明身处此地
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.11,0:04:04.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,却又无影无踪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.72,0:04:07.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看上去就是如此
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.80,0:04:08.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 奥兹
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.22,0:04:12.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你到底在哪里呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.19,0:04:17.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎 你眼中的我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.66,0:04:21.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和布雷克眼中的倒是一样嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.14,0:04:22.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一样的眼神
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.77,0:04:30.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.67,0:04:33.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可以哦 笑脸猫
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.01,0:04:35.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可以杀掉这孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.86,0:04:38.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杀了他的话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.91,0:04:41.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最受伤害的会是谁呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.65,0:04:43.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好好想想吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.69,0:04:46.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.01,0:04:51.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.34,0:04:54.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,另一位客人在呼唤你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.99,0:04:56.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笑脸猫
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.12,0:05:13.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奥兹!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.22,0:05:16.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,基尔!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.87,0:05:18.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了 你没事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.62,0:05:20.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的伤呢 你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.64,0:05:21.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还活着吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.68,0:05:22.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 基尔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.16,0:05:25.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别拽啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.71,0:05:31.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.07,0:05:33.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.00,0:05:36.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又不是什么严重的伤
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.80,0:05:46.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们这样正式的见面
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.99,0:05:48.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是第一次吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.10,0:05:51.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奥兹
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.90,0:05:53.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.61,0:05:58.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出现在艾丽丝记忆中的…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.54,0:06:06.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是谁!?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.13,0:06:09.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想知道的事还有很多吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.59,0:06:10.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.92,0:06:13.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在没有时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.95,0:06:17.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你能否借给我力量
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.54,0:06:20.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想救艾丽丝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.13,0:06:24.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不快一点的话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.85,0:06:27.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她就会被这个空间吞噬
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.72,0:06:28.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,失去一切
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.06,0:06:30.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后被消灭
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.90,0:06:33.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我该怎么做
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.30,0:06:35.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奥兹…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.54,0:06:40.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你 奥兹
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.27,0:06:43.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,首先要找到她
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.61,0:06:46.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想着艾丽丝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.35,0:06:49.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后呼唤她
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.11,0:06:50.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.18,0:06:52.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正因为是你才能做到
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.38,0:06:56.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有你能找到她
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.49,0:06:58.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.45,0:06:59.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我试试看
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.20,0:07:04.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾丽丝…艾丽丝…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.97,0:07:07.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾丽丝…!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.95,0:07:17.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里就是那个男人的记忆所创造的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.42,0:07:20.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.17,0:07:23.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,扎克斯哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.42,0:07:40.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里还是笑脸猫的领地吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.90,0:07:43.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他不会追过来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.43,0:07:44.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用担心
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.27,0:07:46.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在笑脸猫应该被另一位客人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.50,0:07:50.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,占据着思维
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.48,0:07:51.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,布雷克吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.67,0:07:52.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么那家伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.17,0:07:55.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为他拥有的力量很可怕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.54,0:07:58.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无论是对于笑脸猫
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.75,0:08:00.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是对于阿嵬茨的意志而言
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.36,0:08:05.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那种力量毋庸置疑是种威胁
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.75,0:08:11.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.37,0:08:16.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么笑脸猫要保护阿嵬茨的意志呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.14,0:08:22.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定是…他想成为
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.11,0:08:28.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,守护重要之人的唯一的骑士
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.67,0:08:33.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像是对于艾丽丝而言的你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.98,0:08:34.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.30,0:08:37.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可不是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.27,0:08:41.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 你为什么想救艾丽丝
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.02,0:08:45.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对你而言 「艾丽丝」意味着什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.03,0:08:50.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,意味着什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.91,0:08:59.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.50,0:09:02.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾丽丝对于我而言
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.00,0:09:06.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是如同太阳般的存在吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.52,0:09:09.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想哭的时候就哭
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.58,0:09:11.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想生气的时候就生气
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.18,0:09:15.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她总是很坦率地表达自己的感情
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.36,0:09:20.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得她很耀眼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.24,0:09:23.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奥兹
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.80,0:09:25.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没有任何力量
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.66,0:09:27.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.90,0:09:30.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大概无法成为艾丽丝的骑士
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.72,0:09:36.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 那道光究竟能照亮什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.28,0:09:37.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想看到最后
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.48,0:09:39.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在她身边
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.68,0:09:41.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奥兹
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.41,0:09:45.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 我必须去接艾丽丝
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.15,0:09:54.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找到艾丽丝了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.21,0:09:58.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奥兹 艾丽丝就拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.19,0:10:01.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她可是非常讨厌寂寞的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.98,0:10:04.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.49,0:10:08.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为小兔子一寂寞就会死掉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.96,0:10:10.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奥兹
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.17,0:10:13.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你干了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.84,0:10:15.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把奥兹弄哪里去了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.65,0:10:16.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾丽丝的身边
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.17,0:10:18.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为何让他一个人去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.84,0:10:23.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我并不能在这个空间为所欲为
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.87,0:10:27.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能使用的力量是受到限制的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.05,0:10:27.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.16,0:10:29.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为不管怎么说
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.83,0:10:32.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是艾丽丝记忆的一部分呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.37,0:10:34.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你到底是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.63,0:10:37.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是残片
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.36,0:10:40.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,留在艾丽丝记忆中
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.82,0:10:45.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杰克·贝萨流士灵魂的残片
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.61,0:10:52.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,终于来了吗 笨猫
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.74,0:10:54.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.81,0:11:24.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是不故意被你抓到
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.63,0:11:29.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这只胆小的猫咪 绝不会出现在我面前的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.64,0:11:36.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我在你身上
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.64,0:11:40.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,留下名为自知之明的刻印吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.48,0:11:45.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没必要担心哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.48,0:11:48.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是这只眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.01,0:11:51.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为你让它看到不愉快的梦境
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.99,0:11:54.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,特地给你的奖励呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.03,0:11:58.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,疯帽子!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.59,0:12:01.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来吧 调教的时间到了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.51,0:12:22.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.44,0:12:23.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾丽丝
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.69,0:12:28.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾丽丝
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.40,0:12:32.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在哪里 艾丽丝
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.36,0:12:34.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾丽丝
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.01,0:12:59.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾丽丝
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.52,0:13:01.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在哪里 艾丽丝
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.12,0:13:33.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这…这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.09,0:13:37.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你所在的地方 是沙布利耶
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.29,0:13:39.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说 沙布利耶
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.70,0:13:40.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.80,0:13:42.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对你们而言
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.32,0:13:43.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既是曾经的首都
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.10,0:13:47.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也是被巴司卡瓦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.49,0:13:49.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,推入阿嵬茨的城市
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.99,0:13:54.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道 这就是100年前的…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.02,0:13:56.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沙布利耶的悲剧!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.84,0:14:12.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎 可是听说是因为大地震…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.03,0:14:14.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.64,0:14:17.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,表面上是这样掩饰的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.41,0:14:19.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 为何我会在沙布利耶
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.46,0:14:20.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这种地方!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.90,0:14:25.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为这空间是由艾丽丝的记忆创造出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.77,0:14:28.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道 也就是说…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.52,0:14:31.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 她曾在那里
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.98,0:14:34.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,100年前的那天
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.07,0:14:37.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,坐落于悲剧中心的那座城堡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.40,0:14:44.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是艾丽丝最想消除的记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.50,0:14:46.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是这么回事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.93,0:14:49.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾丽丝看到了这种情景吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.66,0:14:50.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.59,0:14:52.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不快点找到她的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.65,0:14:53.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾丽丝
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.10,0:14:55.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾丽丝
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.12,0:15:00.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,继续刚才的话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.75,0:15:03.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把我送到奥兹的身边
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.30,0:15:04.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,立刻!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.02,0:15:11.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没想到会有被你用枪指着的一天呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.02,0:15:25.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 基尔巴特
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.50,0:15:28.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真的忘记了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.73,0:15:31.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.72,0:15:33.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那天的事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.66,0:15:34.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那一切…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.73,0:15:46.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,血的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.45,0:15:50.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无论走到哪儿都是遍地尸体
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.46,0:15:59.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小孩? 还活着?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.86,0:16:01.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没有做错
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.13,0:16:05.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这不是我的错
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.93,0:16:12.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,金色与酒红色的双色眼瞳
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.75,0:16:13.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.86,0:16:16.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有这种可能
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.47,0:16:19.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为这是在100年前的记忆里
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.10,0:16:22.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没有错
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.78,0:16:27.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是…只是为了基尔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.51,0:16:28.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,基尔?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.60,0:16:33.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然是…文森特
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.23,0:16:46.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无论天空 人群 还是我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.80,0:16:48.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都是鲜红的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.70,0:16:54.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.76,0:16:56.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一点都没错
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.96,0:16:57.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.86,0:17:00.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全部都是那家伙的错!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.50,0:17:02.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全都是那家伙的错!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.40,0:17:06.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,文森特!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.94,0:17:21.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.24,0:17:23.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会这样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.59,0:17:26.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果说那真的是文森特的话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.33,0:17:27.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙也是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.92,0:17:31.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,基尔也是100年以前的人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.09,0:17:40.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.63,0:17:45.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么「基尔是100年前的人」啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.62,0:17:47.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我到底在胡思乱想什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.42,0:17:48.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那种事怎么可…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.60,0:18:00.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我 我不就是那样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.89,0:18:02.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我从过去而来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.91,0:18:04.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跨越了10年的时间
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.36,0:18:08.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿嵬茨是时间错乱的空间
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.17,0:18:10.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算成功逃离
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.47,0:18:13.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也不一定能回到原来的时间
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.04,0:18:16.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沙布利耶的悲剧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.26,0:18:20.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,100年前 首都沙布利耶
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.12,0:18:24.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被巴司卡瓦亲手推入阿嵬茨
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.99,0:18:26.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后15年前
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.99,0:18:29.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在贝萨流士家的庭院里
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.23,0:18:30.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发现浑身是伤的基尔
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.22,0:18:34.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以及同样浑身是伤 被奈特雷伊家保护的文森特
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.04,0:18:38.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果那两人在此的话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.99,0:18:41.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同城镇一起被阿嵬茨吞噬
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.59,0:18:45.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后通过某种方法逃到了未来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.56,0:18:48.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这并非不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.35,0:18:53.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我什么都记不起来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.80,0:18:57.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么都不想去记起来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.86,0:19:01.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.01,0:19:04.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,确实不想去记起来呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.35,0:19:08.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起 基尔
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.53,0:19:11.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想不起来也没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.49,0:19:16.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那天的事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.98,0:19:20.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无论对于你还是艾丽丝
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.51,0:19:23.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都留下了无法消失的伤痛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.02,0:19:39.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙 到处乱跑
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.14,0:19:44.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在做什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.88,0:19:46.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明必须先找到艾丽丝
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.33,0:19:49.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在基尔和文森特的事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.24,0:19:50.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都是第二位的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.35,0:19:52.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知为何
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.56,0:19:54.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像是必须要追上他一样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.84,0:19:59.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奥兹正不断跑向艾丽丝
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.97,0:20:01.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,命运…不
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.10,0:20:03.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该说是必然的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.07,0:20:05.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,必然?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.78,0:20:07.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是奥兹
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.50,0:20:09.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾丽丝是染血黑兔
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.10,0:20:13.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,维系着他们的锁链是无法斩断的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.78,0:20:30.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.33,0:20:32.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从刚才开始
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.38,0:20:33.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,胸中就不能平静
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.39,0:20:55.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我 知道这里
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.70,0:20:57.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奥兹
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.10,0:20:59.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是艾丽丝的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.98,0:21:02.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在上面吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.65,0:21:11.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奥兹
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.49,0:21:12.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾丽丝
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.08,0:21:17.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾丽丝!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.68,0:21:47.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奥兹
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.04,0:21:51.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了你以后也能留在艾丽丝身边
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.26,0:21:53.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我认为你应该知道
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.85,0:21:55.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,直到那一刻之前
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.31,0:21:57.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她还是人类
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.92,0:22:03.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,直到100年前
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.78,0:22:07.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她此地被杀害之前
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.92,0:23:42.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,300)\3c&H000000&}你对我而言是特别的……
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.84,0:23:45.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,300)\3c&H000000&}这难道是奥兹干的吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.30,0:23:49.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,300)\3c&H000000&}那些让艾丽丝悲伤的 让艾丽丝受伤的——
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.31,0:23:53.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,300)\3c&H000000&}我要把他们全部毁掉
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.73,0:23:57.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,300)\3c&H000000&}听话的棋子真是帮大忙了 卖帽子的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.15,0:24:00.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,300)\3c&H000000&}我比任何人都……
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.19,0:24:04.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,300)\3c&H000000&}害怕我自己
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.78,0:24:09.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\3c&H000000&}下回 为谁诉说
